defaultt
defaultee 
default(PASC) 
defaultwill no doubt be aware of some of the key background material to this Inquiry, including the Home Office proposals and consultation on crime outcome, the UK Statistics Authority consultation on aligning the Code of Practice, and recent HMIC Inspection repo
defaultrts on police crime recording – the most recent 
default‘The Crime Scene’ dating to January 2012.   This latter report in particular has guided some of the answers set out below in relation to the understanding of the accuracy of crime data.  We believe that HMIC 
defaultwill shortly start a Data Quality inspection, which will look again at crime recording data in forces and may provide some interesting insights into some of the questions posed by the Inquiry.  
