default, 
defaultand that it was a key factor in how they held the
defaultir
default force to account.  They acknowledge there are problems with comparability (for r
defaulteasons already discussed), but at least some PCCs felt that the key issues was whether it met the needs of local communities, not necessarily national policy makers.  
default&#xa0;
defaultThere was some feeling that the 
defaultreal question here was whether the public had confidence in the data, and whether something should be done to improve their perception of statistics.  
defaultThere was also some concern that there is anecdotal evidence that some crimes, including serious crimes a
defaultre not reported by the public and some thought is needed as to how communities can be encouraged to fully report crime.
