defaultQ6
default              
defaultShould recorded crime statistics be classified as National Statistics?
default&#xa0;
defaultThere were mixed feeling on this amongst the PCCs that 
defaultresponded.  Some thought they should as it would help with perceptions of independence, one thought this could only really work for long term trends, but others thought this should be substantially a local issue and the
defaultrefore not a National Statistic.
